Create 2 projects
In the 1st project,choose post build options and choose build other project
and then select the 2nd project there 



Download the build pipeline plugin from manage jenkins - this is one way to do it

Click on + icon on the right of All tab in the dashboard to create a view
Choose create a pipeline by choosing build pipeline view

Now goto select initial job and choose the 1st job
Now save it and trigger the pipeline
This will now create a build and create a WAR or JAR file

This can now be deployed to the test environment